text:
Truly handmade baos and dimsum, will see the staff chopping ingredients and stuffing the buns everytime I go.

Must order from the stall are: Siew Mai, Fan Choy (superb unlike the types you get from coffeeshop drinks stall), the usual charsiu and daosa buns and their Pork Da Pao 大包 (filling to bun ratio is insane).
Handmade Pau! Much much better than Tiong Bahru Pau

Oct 2020 Revisit: found their little Coffee Bun to be the BOMB!

6 months prior review: Nice little stall at the HDB block. Like the char siew bao, siew mai, glutinous rice and har gao that I got.
Very delicious bao! Don't know about it being handmade, but plenty of filling compared to the skin.
